Psalm 34/XX/PR

/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. This psalm is an alphabetical acrostic. The English equiva-
lents of the initial letters are based on the Hebrew, rather than the English,
alphabet. The Tetragrammaton appears in this psalm, as in Psalm 29,
eighteen times, the numerical equivalent of life.    /SC/XXJ.R./XX/PR

